```javascript
function createForm() {
  // Create form
  var form = FormApp.create('Personal Relationship with Technology Survey');

  // Add the questions
  var multipleChoiceItems = [
    {title: "Personal Device Use", choices: ["Less than 1 hour", "1-2 hours", "2-4 hours", "4-6 hours", "More than 6 hours"]},
    {title: "Primary Digital Activity", choices: ["Social Media", "Gaming", "Watching Videos/Streaming", "Reading/Researching", "Other"]},
    {title: "Social Media Platforms", choices: ["TikTok", "Instagram", "Facebook", "Twitter", "Snapchat", "None/Other"]},
    {title: "Current Events Awareness", choices: ["Always", "Often", "Sometimes", "Rarely", "Never"]},
    {title: "Perceived Influence of Ads", choices: ["Strongly Agree", "Agree", "Neutral", "Disagree", "Strongly Disagree"]},
    {title: "Online Peer Interaction", choices: ["Daily", "Weekly", "Monthly", "Rarely", "Never"]},
    {title: "Digital Content Creation", choices: ["Regularly", "Occasionally", "Rarely", "Never"]},
    {title: "Perceived Impact on Mood", choices: ["Mostly Positive", "Somewhat Positive", "Neutral", "Somewhat Negative", "Mostly Negative"]},
    {title: "Privacy Concerns", choices: ["Very Concerned", "Somewhat Concerned", "Neutral", "Not Very Concerned", "Not Concerned at All"]},
    {title: "Digital Breaks", choices: ["Frequently", "Occasionally", "Rarely", "Never"]}
  ];

  for (var i = 0; i < multipleChoiceItems.length; i++) {
    var item = multipleChoiceItems[i];
    var mcItem = form.addMultipleChoiceItem();
    mcItem.setTitle(item.title)
          .setChoiceValues(item.choices);
  }

  // Log the URL of the form
  Logger.log('Form created with URL: ' + form.getPublishedUrl());
}
```

To use this:

1. Open a new Google Sheets document.
2. From the menu, select `Extensions` > `Apps Script`.
3. In the Apps Script editor, erase any code in the code.gs window and paste the script provided above.
4. Save and run the `createForm` function.
5. You may be prompted to give permissions to the script.
6. Once completed, it should create a new Google Form with your questions.

Remember, the permissions are essential, so ensure you grant them when prompted.

